des:
APEXTIME Intelligent Platform, easily control the CHAOS Smart Box and enter your collection community!
1. Support remote control, worry and power saving, and drive whenever and wherever you want;
2. Support intelligent control and more dimensional DIY static and dynamic lighting effects;
3. Support personalized customization, no matter the wind or rain, sunrise or sunset, the lighting can be predicted intelligently;
4. Support multi intelligent box linkage to realize the dynamic light effect of multi box linkage;
5. Easy connection: easily and quickly connect App to devices.

You can simply ask Alexa to control your smart devices. After connecting Alexa to your products in a few simple steps:
(1). Download our “APEXTIME” app in app market then register an account;
(2). Configure our devices in our “APEXTIME” app and change appropriate name for your devices;
(3). Download Amazon "Alexa" app from android,ios or Amazon app market then configure Echo with "Alexa" app;
(4). Search “APEXTIME” skill from the "Alexa" app skills category;
(5). Enable “APEXTIME” skill, and you'll be navigated to “APEXTIME” login page;
(6). Follow the instructions on the page to complete linking;
(7). Now all setup is finished. You can enjoy the voice control on your home devices like these:
“Alexa, turn on the bedroom light.”
“Alexa, turn off the bedroom light.”
“Alexa, set the bedroom light to 50%.”
“Alexa, brighten the bedroom light to 50%.”
“Alexa, dim the bedroom light to 50%.”
"Alexa, set bedroom light to green."
"Alexa, set bedroom light to cool white."
